title: Walkabout: Ash Closes Indonesia Airports; Tunisia Exodus
text:
Eruption Ash from Mount Raung, a volcano in East Java, Indonesia, has closed three regional airports, including one in Bali, typically a popular summer destination for Australians. (BBC News)
